ZH: 我买了一种止血药，以备不时之需。
EN: I bought some hemostatic medicine for emergencies.

ZH: 他被割伤了，需要急需的止血措施。
EN: He got cut and needs immediate hemostatic measures.

ZH: 这种药效果很好，可以快速止血。
EN: This medicine works well and can stop bleeding quickly.

ZH: 他不小心割到手指，急忙用纱布止血。
EN: He accidentally cut his finger and quickly used gauze to stop the bleeding.

ZH: 医生使用止血药帮助手术结束后止血。
EN: The doctor used hemostatic medication to stop bleeding after the surgery.

ZH: 如果伤口过深，应该送医院进行缝合和止血处理。
EN: If the wound is deep, you should go to the hospital for stitching and hemostasis.

ZH: 在急救现场，医护人员使用止血器材进行止血。
EN: At the scene of the emergency, medical staff use hemostatic equipment to stop bleeding.

ZH: 如果出现严重出血，请迅速进行止血处理。
EN: If there is severe bleeding, please perform hemostasis immediately.

ZH: 他的外伤并不严重，只需要使用外用止血药。
EN: His external injury is not severe, he only needs to use topical hemostatic medicine.

ZH: 这种止血药具有较长的效果，并能有效促进伤口愈合。
EN: This hemostatic medicine has a long-lasting effect and can effectively promote wound healing.

ZH: 他在意外中失血过多，需要迅速止血补充体液。
EN: He lost too much blood in the accident and needs quick hemostasis and fluid replacement.

ZH: 大量出血时，除了止血，还要监测血压和心率。
EN: When there is massive bleeding, apart from hemostasis, blood pressure and heart rate should also be monitored.

ZH: 在紧急情况下，压迫伤口能帮助止血。
EN: In emergency situations, applying pressure to the wound can help stop bleeding.

ZH: 医生对伤口进行了止血处理，并使用缝合线对伤口进行缝合。
EN: The doctor performed hemostasis on the wound and used sutures to close it.

ZH: 过敏体质的人易出现止血困难。
EN: People with allergies are prone to difficulties in hemostasis.

ZH: 心脏手术后需要进行严格的止血处理以避免并发症。
EN: Strict hemostasis is required after heart surgery to prevent complications.

ZH: 当伤口不断渗血时，应及时采取止血措施。
EN: When the wound keeps bleeding, hemostasis measures should be taken promptly.

ZH: 医生对伤口进行了止血处理以避免感染。
EN :The doctor performed hemostasis on the wound to avoid infection.

ZH: 这种止血药具有很好的抗菌作用。
EN: This hemostatic medicine has strong antibacterial properties.

ZH: 如果出现长时间的不停止血，请立即就医。
EN: If bleeding does not stop for a prolonged period, seek medical attention immediately.
